Subject: Of Gods, Heroes and Their Foes...
Description: Did you think 'Thor: The Dark World' was awful?  What would you like to see happen in 'X-Men: Days of Future Past'?  What would you have done differently regarding 'Captain America: Winter Solider'?  If these are questions you think about, then please join us for a rousing discussion of the movies and comics alike!   Interested in learning more about Marvel (and yes, DC) comics?  That's why we're here!  Note: there will be free comics and goodies giveaways!         Speakers include:LadyAna, Professor X    - Track: Film  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
